Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back David, don't hurry. We're in Excelsis, Dio. It is of course a great pleasure. I see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We always start with the end of the lecture first, so you don't have to bother listening in the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,meantime. Witness that all things are happening spontaneously. Everything is happening in and of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,its own nature as a consequence of that which it is, not as a consequence of that which it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which implies the duality of a doer and the action. Everything is within an infinite field
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of power. The power is so immense that it escapes the capacity of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to comprehend it because it's invisible, all present, just like people are not aware of gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without which everybody in Australia would fall off the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They do seem strange, too, because they're standing on their heads their whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So I try to correlate the scientific modern mind, reason, and logic with spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,truth, and merge the two so that it's comprehensible from either direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, the world of science stops here, and the world of spirituality starts here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and they really don't have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have any dialogue. They have attempts at it, called science and religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,science and consciousness. And if you listen carefully, you realize, what is the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,between science and religion? There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the relationship between science and consciousness? There isn't any. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do try to merge the two because the modern spiritual truth is heard differently by the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,modern mind than it was many centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it was taken on an, ooh, faith kind of a basis, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have the modern mind to contend with, so it's both a help and a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In a group like this, I advise skipping the mind altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I just tell you what's happening, and all you have to do is notice it, you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,have to think about it, although later we'll explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of everything is what it is. That is its meaning. Its meaning is what
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of a giraffe? The meaning of a giraffe is to be a giraffe. What did
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you think it meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In this infinite field, which is beyond all dimensions and all description, of infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what is being manifested as actuality when conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're witnessing is potentiality continuously emerging as creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, creation and evolution are one and the same thing because evolution is creation.
