Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,changing. It's just emerging into positionalities. So you see the actualization of the potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening in and of its own as a consequence of that which it is. There's no doer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,causing it. The difficulty in a group like this, which is erudite spiritually speaking,
