Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To get beyond cause and effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,one sees that existence is continuously miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness the evolution unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're witnessing the unfolding of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not witnessing cause and effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not witnessing change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not witnessing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all mentalizations that you project.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Descartes was a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And he pointed out the duality of res interna, res cogitans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that is, that which is of the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and res externa, otherwise known as res extensa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the world the way it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the difficulty then in spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to presume that res interna is the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is representing res externa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That how you see the world is the way it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, that's an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As you watch the commentators on the nightly news,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, thank God, mentalization is just,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only res interna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it means surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surrendering the illusion that you're the cause of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the ego, out of its evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,because of its evolution, presumes not only is it cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is the source of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a confrontation that comes near the end of the pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and which we've talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, as a student, should know what's ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because ahead may become this moment within seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I won't have to look at that one for 20, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a cup of tea, and suddenly, the personal you disappears.
