Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then arises the last decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The last decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell that in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we do everything backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's been doing everything forwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see where it's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It took us centuries to move up one or two points in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to start from the ending, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't project thinkingness onto the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and become dumb like a bunny,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then you just see phenomena are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to invent a mystical you that's causing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of causality out there, sociologic theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is what it is, as a consequence of what it has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the pathway, and I'm finishing a book called Transcending the Levels of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's taken me through all these levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the levels disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken me through all those levels again, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And in doing it, we presented the dualities that hold each level of consciousness where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Every level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflects an aversion and an attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the duality of the aversion and the attraction is a perceptual illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see through it and drop it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you instantly move to a different level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did the dualities for the lower levels of consciousness from...
