Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.46,1:37:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,self-destructed.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.46,1:37:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.46,1:37:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the left brain then,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.46,1:37:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,here's your animal brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.56,1:37:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the animal brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.56,1:37:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done this before,
