Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.77,1:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a wholly different
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.77,1:37:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,brain function.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.77,1:37:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the animal brain,
