Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.77,1:37:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,goes to another brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.77,1:37:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then goes to
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.77,1:37:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,another brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.77,1:37:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then goes to
