Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.77,1:37:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,goes to emotions,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.77,1:37:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and stores that in memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.77,1:37:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200,
