Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.52,1:38:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's associated with
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.52,1:38:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain of longing
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.55,1:38:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or regretting.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.55,1:38:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So they never really
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.55,1:38:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,get to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.89,1:38:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200 now,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.89,1:38:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the input
