Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.89,1:38:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see something
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.89,1:38:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of great importance,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.89,1:38:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.89,1:38:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.89,1:38:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal does not
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.89,1:38:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.89,1:38:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.89,1:38:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked this over
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.31,1:38:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.31,1:38:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I discovered that
