Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.67,1:38:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.03,1:38:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.39,1:38:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to have spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.73,1:38:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens at 200 then,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.73,1:38:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by intention
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.73,1:38:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and invocation,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.73,1:38:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.77,1:38:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you now pull into yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.77,1:38:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.77,1:38:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.77,1:38:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it shifts you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.77,1:38:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to the right side
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.77,1:38:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of your brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.77,1:38:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the fast track
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.77,1:39:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is through your
