Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.77,1:39:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the frontal cortex,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.77,1:39:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,through your intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.77,1:39:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and especially
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.77,1:39:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,through your spiritual awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.77,1:39:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very fast
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.77,1:39:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to the emotional center.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.77,1:39:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.77,1:39:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the animal response.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.77,1:39:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the animal response.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.56,1:39:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody cuts in
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.56,1:39:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of you in traffic,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.56,1:39:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you son of a bitch,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.56,1:39:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get even with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.56,1:39:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go home
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.56,1:39:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and you tell your wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.56,1:39:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,boy, he was an SLB, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.85,1:39:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.03,1:39:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with the development
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.03,1:39:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the etheric brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.56,1:39:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this is no longer satisfactory
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.56,1:39:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.56,1:39:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.56,1:39:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what the hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.56,1:39:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,give the guy a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.56,1:39:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You give the guy a break,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.56,1:39:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,let him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.56,1:39:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're delayed
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.56,1:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,two seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.56,1:39:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,getting to the grocery store.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.06,1:39:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not on your way
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.06,1:39:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to a fire
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.06,1:39:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or catching a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.06,1:39:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All the indignation,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.06,1:39:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you think people
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.06,1:39:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are going someplace important,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.06,1:39:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.06,1:39:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to pick up
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.06,1:39:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a Pepsi at the nearest
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.06,1:39:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,mini-mart.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.47,1:39:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And this tremendous
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.47,1:39:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,rush of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.47,1:39:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and energy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.47,1:40:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and energy
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.55,1:40:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is tremendous rush.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.55,1:40:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see him
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.55,1:40:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,like this
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.55,1:40:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you pass him
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.55,1:40:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and there he is,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.55,1:40:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he's getting a Coke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.55,1:40:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Risking his life,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.55,1:40:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's life,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.55,1:40:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,risking his driver's license,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.55,1:40:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,getting points,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.55,1:40:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,running up his insurance bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.55,1:40:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's run
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.55,1:40:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with this here,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.55,1:40:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvey Wallbanger.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.64,1:40:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember the days
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.25,1:40:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the CBs?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.25,1:40:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.25,1:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my old truck,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.25,1:40:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.25,1:40:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I drove all over the place
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.25,1:40:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in my old truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.47,1:40:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'd hear
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.47,1:40:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.47,1:40:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a Harvey Wallbanger
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.47,1:40:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,coming in east on 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.47,1:40:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvey Wallbanger
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.47,1:40:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,was a guy who was driving
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.47,1:40:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,like 85,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.47,1:40:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.47,1:40:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and going up on two wheels.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.47,1:40:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He always had a red car,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.47,1:40:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a red car.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.18,1:40:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the insurance
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.18,1:40:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,rates are always higher
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.18,1:40:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on red cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.18,1:40:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.18,1:40:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.18,1:40:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they're higher on a red car,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.34,1:40:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.34,1:40:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.34,1:40:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so because it tends
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.34,1:40:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to pull up the left brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.10,1:40:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this brain will let
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.10,1:40:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody in
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.10,1:40:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.10,1:41:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,give the guy a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.10,1:41:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.10,1:41:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.10,1:41:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you got left brain dominance
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.10,1:41:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're being run
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.10,1:41:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.06,1:41:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You also tend to run out
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.06,1:41:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the neurotransmitters
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.06,1:41:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you need Prozac
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.06,1:41:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,after a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.56,1:41:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.56,1:41:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the right brain dominates.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.56,1:41:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.56,1:41:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it enjoys peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.67,1:41:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,positive emotion,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.67,1:41:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,increased immunity,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.67,1:41:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a balanced acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.69,1:41:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.69,1:41:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.69,1:41:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.76,1:41:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.76,1:41:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.76,1:41:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.76,1:41:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.76,1:41:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds so Sanskrit,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.76,1:41:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.76,1:41:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it sounds so old Hindu
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.76,1:41:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sanskrit-y
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.76,1:41:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's really hard
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.76,1:41:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for an American
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.76,1:41:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy a Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.76,1:41:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to invent
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.76,1:41:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.76,1:41:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just call it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.76,1:41:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual energy.
